headline: KKR & Co. Inc. to Announce Third Quarter 2025 Results
summary: NEW YORK, October 02, 2025--KKR & Co. Inc. (NYSE: KKR) announced today that it plans to release its financial results for the third quarter 2025 on Friday, November 7, 2025, before the opening of trading on the New York Stock Exchange.
